---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Kitchen Remodeling"
  description={`Kitchen remodeling in Asheville & Hendersonville, NC: sinks, appliances, countertops, cabinets and full kitchen plumbing. Call ${site.phone} for a free estimate.`}
  heroTitle="How to Fall in Love With Your Kitchen"
  heroSubtitle="Hire a kitchen remodel plumber in Asheville or Hendersonville, NC."
  heroImage="/images/gallery/gallery-07.jpg"
  listHeading="We install everything your kitchen needs"
  listItems={[
    'Update old, boring or rusted sinks.',
    'Install the latest dishwashers and appliances.',
    'Replace dated countertops, kitchen tile and cabinets.',
    'Handle any kitchen plumbing issue.',
  ]}
  listNote="From plumbing to contracting, we do it all. Call us today to make sure it's done right the first time."
  ctaHeading="Ready to Love Your Kitchen Again?"
>
  <p>
    A good kitchen is the one you never want to leave. Nesbitt's Plumbing gets you there by
    updating tired appliances and fixtures and rebuilding the plumbing behind them. Our licensed
    kitchen remodel plumbers work throughout Asheville and Hendersonville, NC, and we finish
    residential and commercial jobs cleanly, with no drawn-out hassle.
  </p>
  <p>
    From plumbing to contracting, we do it all, and we've been remodeling kitchens across Western
    North Carolina for years.
  </p>
  <p>
    Contact us today at
    <a href={site.phoneHref} class="font-semibold text-drop-600 hover:underline">{site.phone}</a>
    so our experienced plumbers and contractors can help you design a kitchen you love spending
    time in.
  </p>
</ServiceLayout>
